translation[9]{c,v,t}:
  39,32,Uss say barh ker zalim kon hai jo Allah Taalaa per jhoot bolay? Aur sacha deen jab uss kay pass aaye to ussay jhoota bataye? Kiya aisay kuffaar kay liye jahannum thikana nahi hai
  39,33,Aur jo sachay deen ko laye aur jiss ney iss ki tasdeeq ki yehi log paarsa hain
  39,34,Unn kay liye unn kay rab kay pass (her) woh cheez hai jo yeh chahyen nek logon ka yeh hi badla hai
  39,35,Takay Allah Taalaa unn say unn kay buray amalon ko door ker dey aur jo nek kaam unhon ney kiyey hain unn ka acha badla ata farmaye
  39,36,Kiya Allah Taalaa apnay bandon kay liye kafi nahi? Yeh log aap ko Allah kay siwa auron say dara rahey hain aur jissay Allah gumrah ker day uss ki rehnumaee kerney wala koi nahi
  39,37,Aur jissay woh hidayat day ussay koi gumrah kerney wala nahi kiya Allah Taalaa ghalib aur badla lenay wala nahi hai
  39,38,Agar aap inn say poochen kay aasman-o-zamin ko kiss ney peda kiya hai? To yaqeenan woh yehi jawab den gay kay Allah ney. Aap inn kahiyey acha yeh to batao jinhen tum Allah kay siwa pukartay ho agar Allah Taalaa mujhay nuksan phonchana chahye to kiya yeh uss kay nuksan ko hata saktay hain? Ya Allah Taalaa mujh per meharbani ka iradah keray to kiya yeh uss ki meharbani ko rok saktay hain? Aap keh den kay Allah mujhay kafi hai tawakkal kerney walay ussi per tawakkal kertay hain
  39,39,Keh dijiye kay aey meri qom! Tum apni jagah per amal kiye jao mein bhi amal ker raha hun abhi abhi tum jaan lo gay
  39,40,Kay kiss per ruswa kerney wala azab aata hai aur kiss per daeemi maar aur hameshgi ki saza hoti hai